Package: filtertools
Type: Package
Title: Simple and Intuitive Data Filtering Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Geordie", "McRuer",
                  email = "geordie.mcruer@ontario.ca",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides intuitive wrapper functions around dplyr filtering operations
    for common data filtering tasks. Includes functions for string pattern matching
    (filter_in, filter_out), NA-based filtering (filter_in_na, filter_out_na),
    and numeric value filtering. Designed to make interactive data exploration
    faster and more readable.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 1.0.0),
    stringr,
    magrittr,
    rlang,
    purrr
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/mcruer/filtertools
BugReports: https://github.com/mcruer/filtertools/issues
